{"tid":1596911,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係airdrop收到首歌，歌名叫《香港·革命》","createTime":"2019-09-26T17:07:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T23:55:55.000Z","uid":273821,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cdaac03091737d9d4d176b22545720f4f9ff09e0","tid":1596911,"uid":273821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T17:07:30.000Z","msg":"話說有日行行下街，airdrop收到呢首歌，內容又幾中pt，係講緊香港嘅情況，個旋律又好聽，所以想同大家分享下.<br />\n<br />\n《 香港&middot;革命 》<br />\n<br />\n作曲/填詞：香港人64<br />\n編曲/鋼琴：求其<br />\n<br />\n和你衝 TG一堆飛過橫破了長空<br />\n憑面罩 越過槍雨彈林也絕未敢放鬆<br />\n和你衝 為著香港可有片 自由天空<br />\n流著血 受了傷 也未曾退讓<br />\n同面對 渡過苦 進化成更強<br />\n<br />\nFree Hong Kong <br />\nBe strong<br />\n槍火炮刀也能抵擋<br />\n無懼怕 豁出去 共挽手你我破風破浪<br />\n<br />\nFree Hong kong <br />\nBe strong<br />\n終點勝利已在前方<br />\n全力去 變幻似水 <br />\n定會將 勝利高舉<br />\n<br />\nFree Hong Kong <br />\nBe strong<br />\n槍火炮刀也能抵擋<br />\n無懼怕 豁出去 共挽手你我破風破浪<br />\n<br />\nFree Hong Kong <br />\nBe strong<br />\n終點勝利已在前方<br />\n全力去 變幻似水 結伴沿路同行<br />\n捱下去 用信心 革命抗爭<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/A0FfsfbLlh8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FA0FfsfbLlh8&d=0M2zeZ419d%2BEsiU1FPoAw45RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=e96dc3d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/A0FfsfbLlh8</a>"},{"pid":"95d21e013b704327376f6d005d4d7bee311a5956","tid":1596911,"uid":273821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T17:08:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6691a1beb547268a402acedb2b1dc1e4fd844b9","tid":1596911,"uid":273821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T17:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f454a5dd16ae3540f70d32b27356f2eaad67a486","tid":1596911,"uid":273821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T17:09:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/no